1. Učinio si mi *štetu* kada si slomio moj mobilni telefon. (You caused me *damage* when you broke my mobile phone.)
2. Molim vas da nadoknadite *štetu* koju ste mi naneli vašim neopreznim ponašanjem. (Please compensate for the *damage* you caused me with your careless behavior.)
3. Koliko novca tražiš za *štetu* koju sam ti naneo? (How much money do you want for the *damage* I caused you?)
4. Tokom poplave mnogi ljudi su pretrpeli veliku *štetu* na svojim imanjima. (During the flood, many people suffered great *damage* to their properties.)
5. Ova nova politika može naneti *štetu* poslovanju naše kompanije. (This new policy can cause *damage* to our company's business.)
6. Nemojte se ponašati na način koji može naneti *štetu* drugima. (Do not behave in a way that can cause *damage* to others.)
7. Naš tim je pretrpeo *štetu* kada smo izgubili jednog od najboljih igrača zbog povrede. (Our team suffered *damage* when we lost one of our best players due to injury.)
8. Molim vas da pazite na ovo staklo jer je veoma skupo i ne želim da trpim *štetu*. (Please be careful with this glass because it is very expensive and I do not want to suffer *damage*.)